commit.message:
darwin.h (LINK_SPEC): Pass -nofixprebinding to linker.

gcc
        * config/darwin.h (LINK_SPEC): Pass -nofixprebinding to linker.
        * doc/invoke.texi: Document new Darwin linker option -nofixprebinding.
testsuite
        * gcc.dg/darwin-ld-6.c: New test.

From-SVN: r71259
